            sourceSnippet3: 'Kremlin says Russia\'s peace deal stance unchanged; Zelensky pushes for negotiations — Reuters, 29 Juni 2026',
            source4: 'The Guardian',
            sourceUrl4: 'https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/jun/30/ukraine-war-briefing-zelenskyy-ridicules-russian-military-drive-saying-putin-keeps-postponing-goal-deadlines',
